Create an Enhanced Bot

Use the Guided Setup Flow to create an enhanced bot from scratch or from a template. Or you can clone an existing bot.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Setup for Einstein Bots is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
To use enhanced Messaging channels with Enhanced Bots, view required editions.


USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To build and manage Einstein Bots:	
Customize Application

OR

Modify Metadata

OR

Manage Bots


ROUTING FOR YOUR ENHANCED BOT
Create an Enhanced Bot from Scratch or from a Template	

In the guided setup, you can create or select a default outbound Omni-Channel flow. If you create an outbound flow, it’s saved as Route from [Bot Name] and appears in the Outbound Omni-Channel Flow setting on the Bot Overview page.


Clone a Standard Bot as an Enhanced Bot	

When you clone a standard bot as an enhanced bot, we create a simple inbound Omni-Channel flow for your bot. It’s saved as Route to [Bot Name] and appears in the Inbound Omni-Channel Flows section of the Bot Overview page.


Clone an Enhanced Bot	

When you clone an enhanced bot, the inbound Omni-Channel flows that route conversations to your original bot don’t automatically route conversations to your new bot.

Create an Enhanced Bot from Scratch or from a Template
Use the guided setup to create an enhanced bot from scratch or from a template.
Clone a Standard Bot as an Enhanced Bot
Clone a standard bot as an enhanced bot to upgrade your existing conversation designs with rich content and more flexible routing.
Clone an Enhanced Bot
Create a similar enhanced bot to quickly help with development, or grow your enhanced bot portfolio by creating similar bots for different use cases. You can’t clone an enhanced bot as a standard bot.

Enable and Configure Omni-Channel
Route Conversations to and from Your Enhanced Bot
title: Creating and Managing Enhanced Bots in Service Cloud
